summary: This mod will add allows you to craft Stormcloak armor in forges and anvils.
descriptionHtml:
This mod will add allows you to craft Stormcloak armor in forges and anvils. If you want the Skyrim Special Edition version go [url=http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrimspecialedition/mods/9830?]here[/url]. Also check out my [url=http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/74824/?]Dawnguard Crossbows And Bolts[/url] mod.

Requirements
Skyrim

To install just download then extract folder and drag plugin into your data folder.
author: LegoManIAm94
